"to the\n"
"   server list.\n"
"\n"
"The magnet link must contain the eD2k hash and file length.\n"
msgstr ""
"允许添加的eD2k链接：\n"
"*) 文件链接（ed2k://|file|..），将添加至下载队列，\n"
